{"tid":490732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【打擊避稅】澳門被歐盟列入避稅天堂黑名單 憂隨時被制裁","createTime":"2017-12-06T01:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T01:41:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"911ff659a85b4914375574c547a16ed281275114","tid":490732,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:36:22.000Z","msg":"歐盟財長周二通過避稅天堂黑名單，名單中包括17個國家及地區，指這些國家在稅務問題上並不合作，而澳門亦榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n17個避稅天堂除澳門外，包括美屬薩摩亞、巴林、格林納達、關島、南韓、馬紹爾群島、蒙古、納米比亞、帕勞、巴拿馬、聖盧西亞、薩摩亞、特立尼達和多巴哥、突尼斯和阿聯酋，被列入黑名單的國家可能會受到制裁。<br />\n<br />\n法國財長勒梅爾（Bruno Le Maire）表示，另有47個國家或地區列入「灰名單」，這些國家或地區目前不遵守歐盟的規定，但承諾會修改其稅務條例。<br />\n<br />\n隨著多次離岸避稅天堂事件曝光，歐盟成員國今年二月宣佈推出黑名單，以打擊公司及富豪成立海外空殼公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171205/57545711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57545711&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSabljOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2b9c1a0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57545711&h=2cce8a23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171205/57545711</a>"},{"pid":"1c1b01775873ddd4f3480457f9bb89c36709d44d","tid":490732,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"好快制裁埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 阿姨啲分析果然無錯港澳已被西方視為中國鐵幕一部份"},{"pid":"908b58fe503d5c902cd8b7c087460533a24c7200","tid":490732,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:41:55.000Z","msg":"有人去賭就得，澳特應該未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}